snippet.title: Electrician Simulator - First Shock Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Repair and assemble sockets, panels, strips, plugs, chandeliers and even change light bulbs.
Try out and play for free on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1781160/Electrician_Simulator__First_Shock/ 
Oh... and don't mix up the wires! Results might be shocking. Playable from 6th January 2022 The Electrician Simulator - First Shock is a free to play prologue version of the game.
Join other electricians on our Discord: https://discord.gg/s7WHtmkRQ9

Or check out our shocking social media:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ElectricianSimulator
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ElectricianSim
Publisher Social Media: https://linktr.ee/GamingFactorySA
